high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the black circular table in the corner.
Grab a salt shaker on the table.
Turn around and walk to the black end table.
Place the salt shaker on the black end table.
Turn around and walk to the black circular table in the corner.
Grab a salt shaker on the table.
Turn around and walk to the black end table.
Place the salt shaker on the black end table.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the door, then walk left to the round black table.
Pick up the salt shaker on the left of the other salt shaker.
Turn around and walk to the black table.
Place the shaker on the right front corner of the table.
Turn around and walk back to the round table.
Pick up the salt shaker.
Turn around and walk back to the corner black table.
Place the salt shaker on the back table to the left of the other salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the door, the hang a left and walk up to the black table.
Pick up the leftmost salt shaker off of the black table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and take a step forward, turn left and walk up to the small black shelving unit to the left of the table.
Put the salt shaker on top of the black shelving unit.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn left and walk up to the black table.
Pick up the salt shaker off of the table.
Turn around and walk over to the black shelving unit.
Put the salt shaker on top of the black shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Move two salt shakers to a black shelving unit.
